  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个患者从社区到住院的流程图，重点是展示access block机制——就是床位占满后怎么反向影响急诊。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "Inpatient",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。起点是Community，然后患者通过GP或者直接去ED对吗？GP和ED arrival之间需要连线吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，GP可以转诊到ED，但ED arrival也可以直接来自社区。所以Community要同时连到GP和ED_Arrival，GP再连到ED_Arrival。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Community→GP/primary care，Community→ED arrival，GP→ED arrival，这三条都画好了。接下来是ED评估？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ED_Arrival之后是ED assessment & treatment，然后才是Decision to admit。这个decision节点很重要，是分流点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "ED_Treat连到Decision to admit，然后再到Inpatient stay。这些状态节点我用红色系突出显示？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
