    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，ED_Treat和Inpatient是核心状态。Decision to admit用中性色就行，它只是个决策点。然后Inpatient之后要有一个Ready for discharge。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Inpatient→Ready for discharge画好了。现在到关键部分了——你提到的access block，具体有哪些constraints？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "主要是两个blockages：Aged care placement床位不足，还有NDIS supports/accommodation的延迟或 mismatch。这两个都会卡住出院。",
      "elements_involved": [
